                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Chrome</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>

          

                      <span>
                        <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/CSS/Reference/Values/basic-shape/shape">css ➞ types ➞ basic-shape ➞ shape</a>
                      </span>
                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
              </ol>
	            <h4>HTTP</h4>
              <ol>
                  <li>

          

                      <span>
                        <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/HTTP/Reference/Headers/Accept-Encoding#zstd">http ➞ headers ➞ Accept-Encoding ➞ zstd</a>
                      </span>
                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>

          

                      <span>
                        <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/HTTP/Reference/Headers/Content-Encoding#zstd">http ➞ headers ➞ Content-Encoding ➞ zstd</a>
                      </span>
                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
              </ol>
	            <h4>WEBASSEMBLY</h4>
              <ol>
                  <li>
                      <span>webassembly ➞ api ➞ Memory ➞ toFixedLengthBuffer
                      	<a href="https://webassembly.github.io/spec/js-api/#dom-memory-tofixedlengthbuffer"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>
                      <span>webassembly ➞ api ➞ Memory ➞ toResizableBuffer
                      	<a href="https://webassembly.github.io/spec/js-api/#dom-memory-toresizablebuffer"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

